<lb ed="B" n="0936b16"/>也</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>舳艫</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0936b1604" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">舳音軸船後持柁處艫音盧船頭剌櫂處</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>傀儡</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0936b1622" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">傀苦猥切儡魯猥切</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>摟</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0936b1631" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">力侯
